item.title: Olga Pisarskiy
item.description: Olga has been coaching in the CSRA since moving to the area from Charlotte, NC in 2017. Her experience ranges from coaching Olympic Weightlifting in a class setting, group functional fitness, powerlifting, and a specialization in one-on-one Olympic Weightlifting coaching. Prior to opening a brick and mortar space, Olga was providing remote and in-person coaching as well as individualized programming. She has developed athletes and coached on all competitive levels from local meets to USAW National level events alongside her team; Butcher Barbell. Olga founded North Augusta Barbell after seeing a need for a dedicated Olympic Weightlifting space in the CSRA. Her passion is to grow the sport of Weightlifting and empower athletes to reach their full potential.
